*** RazerS 3 - Faster, fully sensitive read mapping ***
http://www.seqan.de/projects/razers.html

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Table of Contents
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  1.   Overview
  2.   Installation
  3.   Usage
  4.   Output Formats
